outputs.output_descr: Closer cooperation between the UN System in Montenegro and the Government of Montenegro as a result in effective implementation of Delivering As One and Integrated UN Programme 2010-2016. This programme encompasses joint programmes as a way to assist the Government in its EU accession process and enables the environment for successful implementation of UN Eco Shared Premises.

project_descr: UNCT coordination and joint programming, including UN support in implementation of Millennium Declaration, aligning UN programme cycle with national development cycle, UNDAF implementation, UN M& E framework, new joint programmes...
